index 7349def..f4853e8 100644
--- a/hw/xfree86/doc/man/xorg.conf.man.pre
+++ b/hw/xfree86/doc/man/xorg.conf.man.pre
@@ -1537,9 +1537,7 @@ sections have the following format:
